description: [``botocore``] Added parameters to track the data volume in bytes for a member account. Deprecated the existing parameters that tracked the volume as a percentage of the allowed volume for a behavior graph. Changes reflected in MemberDetails object.
[``botocore``] Add operations: AddPartner, DescribePartners, DeletePartner, and UpdatePartnerStatus to support tracking integration status with data partners.
[``botocore``] Support new S3 Recording Config allowing customers to write downlink data directly to S3.
[``botocore``] Amazon Kendra now enables users to override index-level boosting configurations for each query.
[``botocore``] Added support for creating and updating stack sets with self-managed permissions from templates that reference macros.
